WEBVTT


00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.940
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:28.320
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.070
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:42.180
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.990
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.060
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.720
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:56.760 --> 00:00:59.940
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:03.220
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.890
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.920
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.280
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:22.360
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:26.020
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.350
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:33.790
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:35.040
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.900
=Episode 39=

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:39.440
I promise.

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:42.680
I'll never make you cry again.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.400
Sleep now.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:28.760
Marry me.

00:03:02.840 --> 00:03:03.680
For real?

00:03:23.300 --> 00:03:29.300
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:36.520
Stop crowding me.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.680
It feels weird.

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:38.800
Let me breathe.

00:03:39.600 --> 00:03:40.440
No way.

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:42.160
You need to hear what

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:43.440
the people say.

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:44.280
- Exactly.
- Right.

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:45.320
Yeah.

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:48.120
Troupe Leader Yi, you have no idea

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:49.400
while you've been away lately,

00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:51.440
we realized how important you are.

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:53.440
It was chaos without you.

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:54.440
- Exactly.
- Yeah.

00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:56.760
Honestly, all that messy gossip,

00:03:56.760 --> 00:03:58.120
no one really bought it, right?

00:03:58.120 --> 00:04:00.280
Right. Those rumors look fake.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:02.080
Anyone with sense wouldn't believe them.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:03.680
We all believe in you.

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:04.960
- Right.
- Listen.

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:06.080
Focus on rehearsing.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.720
Don't worry about a thing, okay?

00:04:07.720 --> 00:04:09.080
As for Chu Jiahe,

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:10.600
she already admitted it to the boss.

00:04:10.600 --> 00:04:11.560
Admitted what?

00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:13.040
That she made up the rumors.

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:14.800
She said she invented all of it.

00:04:14.800 --> 00:04:16.400
She's envied you since childhood.

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:17.640
She can't stand seeing you do well.

00:04:17.640 --> 00:04:18.720
She tried every way she could

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:20.160
to pin all that dirt on you.

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.160
Don't listen to him.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:23.480
Only his first line was true.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:25.160
The rest was all twisted up.

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:30.200
A lot has happened lately.

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.480
Let's all learn from it.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:34.880
Don't jump at every rumor again.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:37.120
But for now,

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:38.880
our top priority

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:40.240
is getting back on track.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:41.840
Let's get rehearsals going.

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.360
Time won't wait for us.

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:44.640
Right?

00:04:45.080 --> 00:04:46.840
Come on, let's start.

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:48.360
- Okay.
- Come on.

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:49.520
Let's rehearse.

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.280
Let's hurry up.

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:54.360
Troupe Leader.

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:56.960
Qin'e.

00:04:58.040 --> 00:04:58.880
Come here.

00:05:05.760 --> 00:05:07.080
I hear you're getting married.

00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:11.680
Congratulations.

00:05:11.800 --> 00:05:13.840
Liu is a good man.

00:05:14.080 --> 00:05:15.080
You can count on him.

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:16.560
Thanks, Troupe Leader.

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:19.920
I have an idea to run by you.

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:21.200
After you're married,

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:23.920
you can't have kids for a few years.

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:27.240
I... I haven't even planned that yet.

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:28.520
By the time you do,

00:05:28.520 --> 00:05:29.880
I'll be done for.

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:31.520
Think about a whole troupe,

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:34.120
how hard it is to train actors like you.

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:36.120
Chu Jiahe wants to leave.

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:38.640
So tell me, what about the troupe?

00:05:38.640 --> 00:05:40.360
Then we'd have to do all-male opera.

00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:41.560
Chu Jiahe wants to leave?

00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:44.520
She filed a report. It's in my office.

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:45.760
I haven't approved it yet.

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.080
Who is it?

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:53.520
It's me, Yi Qin'e.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:04.920
Why are you here?

00:06:05.280 --> 00:06:06.640
Why not keep singing?

00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:09.240
I'm not in your Youth Troupe.

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:10.080
Stay out of it.

00:06:10.440 --> 00:06:11.480
Either way, I hope you

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:13.000
finish Da Jiao Zan before you go.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.080
Why would you care?

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:19.040
I know it wasn't you.

00:06:19.640 --> 00:06:20.800
No matter how much you hate me,

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:22.160
you'd never do something like that.

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:26.440
How do you know?

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:29.200
If it were you, you
wouldn't have saved me.

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:37.160
Ms. Mi Lan came to see me.

00:06:38.680 --> 00:06:39.760
What did she say?

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:43.600
She said,

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:46.360
"Everyone wants to be the lead,

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:48.440
but most people

00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:50.040
are just background players.

00:06:51.640 --> 00:06:53.400
Once you see yourself as an onlooker,

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:55.400
you'll realize

00:06:55.400 --> 00:06:56.880
everything gets a lot easier."

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:02.800
After all this time,

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:06.600
I realized I'm only an onlooker.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:11.720
Timing, place, and people

00:07:12.760 --> 00:07:13.880
all have to line up

00:07:14.520 --> 00:07:15.800
to make one the lead.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.000
Why?

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.320
Why should timing, place, and people

00:07:21.320 --> 00:07:22.800
never be on my side?

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:26.000
Only the leftovers end up with me.

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:31.000
I'm not as good as you?

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:33.440
I don't accept it.

00:07:34.080 --> 00:07:35.440
I'll never accept it.

00:07:37.320 --> 00:07:38.760
You're just luckier than I am.

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:44.160
Onstage, one may be the lead,

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:47.240
but not always in real life.

00:07:48.440 --> 00:07:49.600
Sometimes,

00:07:50.280 --> 00:07:51.880
the brighter you shine onstage,

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:54.800
the lower you feel after.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:59.160
I'd like to feel that loss.

00:08:00.640 --> 00:08:02.040
Then sing Da Jiao Zan.

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:05.200
Then do whatever comes next, no regrets.

00:08:09.480 --> 00:08:10.680
These past few days...

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:12.400
Rough, huh?

00:08:16.120 --> 00:08:16.960
How about you?

00:08:19.080 --> 00:08:20.480
People love to talk.

00:08:21.160 --> 00:08:22.600
I can't control what they say.

00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:24.640
As for this matter,

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:26.920
someone has to take the hit.

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:28.520
If it's not you,

00:08:29.240 --> 00:08:30.080
then it's me.

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:32.680
That's just how it goes.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.280
So...

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:39.800
It's settled.

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:41.920
You sing Da Jiao Zan.

00:08:41.920 --> 00:08:43.200
I sing Hu Xian Jie.

00:08:43.840 --> 00:08:45.480
We'll make some noise together.

00:08:52.420 --> 00:08:53.820
(Chang'an; Ningzhou)

00:08:53.840 --> 00:08:54.840
Hongbing.

00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:55.920
Come on, come on.

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:56.960
Brother-in-law.

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:58.280
Slow down, easy.

00:08:58.720 --> 00:08:59.800
Brother-in-law, what's this?

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:00.800
So heavy.

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:03.040
It's all good stuff you can't get here.

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:04.720
- Uncle. Auntie.
- Hongbing.

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:05.840
Why are you still calling us

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:06.720
Uncle and Auntie?

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:07.760
It's important.

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:09.800
I should wait until the wedding.

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.680
Then I'll make you both happy.

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:14.200
See how thoughtful Hongbing is?

00:09:14.200 --> 00:09:15.600
- Come on.
- Liu Hongbing.

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:16.720
Where's Laidi?

00:09:17.200 --> 00:09:19.160
She's rehearsing at the provincial troupe.

00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:20.280
I'll take you to the hotel.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:22.000
Why stay at a hotel?

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:24.160
Laidi and her uncle have places.

00:09:24.160 --> 00:09:25.520
We can just stay there.

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:27.080
It's such a small thing.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:29.120
Just listen to the kid.

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:30.000
I'll listen if it's right.

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:31.520
But not if it costs money.

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:33.120
Put them in the car.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.560
- Here, Mom.
- Mom, stop fussing.

00:09:36.640 --> 00:09:38.360
Brother, want some water?

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:40.600
Can this console still play, brother?

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.240
- It's great.
- Of course.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.040
Put this cartridge in.

00:09:44.040 --> 00:09:45.040
- The TV's off.
- Hongbing.

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:46.000
Turn it on.

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.520
- Hongbing, I checked.
- Auntie.

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:49.840
Laidi, Pandi, and I get the big room.

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:51.680
You and your dad take the small room.

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:54.160
Cungen, you and your brother-in-law

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:56.040
can sleep on a floor bed here.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:57.520
Why sleep on the floor?

00:09:57.520 --> 00:09:59.240
Get a room at Beishan Hotel.

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:01.240
That costs money, doesn't it?

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:03.480
Save what we can. Listen to me.

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:04.360
I'm going nowhere.

00:10:04.360 --> 00:10:05.360
I'm staying with Hongbing.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:06.200
Silly.

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:09.040
Fine, I'll sleep on the floor with you.

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:09.880
Hongbing.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:12.880
Hongbing, this cord is too thin.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.480
For the toilet flush, I...

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:15.640
It snapped with one light tug.

00:10:15.640 --> 00:10:17.080
Find a thicker one. I'll replace it.

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:18.680
Uncle, don't bother.

00:10:18.680 --> 00:10:20.400
This lousy cord's been bad for ages.

00:10:20.400 --> 00:10:21.520
- Well...
- I hate it.

00:10:21.520 --> 00:10:22.520
- Use it for now.
- Well...

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:23.560
I'll replace it tomorrow.

00:10:23.560 --> 00:10:25.460
Brother-in-law, where should this go?

00:10:25.460 --> 00:10:26.440
Sis, what's this?

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:27.360
Medicinal herbs.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:29.760
Your brother-in-law and I
got them for Laidi.

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:30.960
Thank you, brother-in-law.

00:10:31.080 --> 00:10:31.920
Brother-in-law. Sis.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:33.440
- Wonderful.
- Great.

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:34.280
Hongbing.

00:10:34.520 --> 00:10:36.800
- Coming!
- Where are your pillows and quilt?

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:39.800
Brother-in-law, why can't I clear this?

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:41.120
- Brother-in-law!
- Wait a sec.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:42.040
I'll figure it out myself.

00:10:42.040 --> 00:10:42.880
Brother-in-law!

00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:45.080
What's so hard about it?

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:47.080
Every level's tough till you beat it.

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:48.920
(Invitation)
Come on, take one.

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:51.720
The wedding banquet's on the 10th.

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:52.880
At Chang'an Restaurant.

00:10:53.640 --> 00:10:55.200
We hired a top chef from Guangdong.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:57.360
Fresh seafood, all you can eat.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.840
Nice.

00:10:59.680 --> 00:11:01.280
When Wang Qinsheng got married last year,

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:03.000
there wasn't even a scrap of grease.

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:04.560
Just a whole table of greens.

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:05.400
Wasn't he worried

00:11:05.400 --> 00:11:06.560
that he'd be a cuckold?

00:11:09.160 --> 00:11:10.920
Director, have a smoke.

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.680
Wishing you both happiness!

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:17.840
The voice even cracked.

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:21.040
(Ticket window)
"Da Jiao Zan", half off!

00:11:21.840 --> 00:11:24.040
"Da Jiao Zan", half off!

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:26.320
Half-price tickets! Half-price!

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:27.160
Want one?

00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:28.680
Half-price!

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:30.840
Got any Hu Xian Jie tickets?

00:11:30.840 --> 00:11:31.920
What are you thinking?

00:11:31.920 --> 00:11:33.520
That sold out ages ago.

00:11:33.520 --> 00:11:34.600
Da Jiao Zan tickets?

00:11:35.080 --> 00:11:35.920
Nope.

00:11:36.520 --> 00:11:38.360
Not as good as Hu Xian Jie.

00:11:47.000 --> 00:12:04.360
♪Marshal's order♪

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.680
♪I hit the kid's head♪

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:00.400
You sang great.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:03.680
You mean it?

00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:09.040
But the play isn't really for you.

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:11.360
You're no kitchen maid.

00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:13.880
You're Cui Yingying.

00:13:14.280 --> 00:13:15.600
You're Princess Shengping.

00:13:16.640 --> 00:13:18.440
You'll never suffer hardship.

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:22.440
I heard you're getting married.

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:27.200
Congrats.

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:30.200
Thanks.

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:33.080
Can you make it?

00:13:33.640 --> 00:13:34.880
Come to our wedding.

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:37.440
I'm leaving the day after tomorrow.

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:39.280
For Shenzhen.

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:41.480
I won't be back.

00:13:42.800 --> 00:13:44.120
Shenzhen...

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.360
That's so far away.

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:50.600
I'm going to be the lead in my life.

00:13:52.680 --> 00:13:53.600
Yi Qin'e.

00:13:57.680 --> 00:13:58.960
Be happy from now on.

00:14:02.960 --> 00:14:04.200
We'll both be happy.

00:14:23.560 --> 00:14:25.360
That night, after the show,

00:14:25.840 --> 00:14:27.400
Chu Jiahe herself

00:14:27.400 --> 00:14:29.600
stood on stage for a long time,

00:14:30.880 --> 00:14:33.040
thinking of her days on stage,

00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:35.400
her joy and sorrow,

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:39.320
and her tears and sweat.

00:14:40.080 --> 00:14:42.800
But Chu Jiahe chose to let go.

00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:46.400
She understood before Yi Qin'e did

00:14:47.080 --> 00:14:49.240
that every show must end someday,

00:14:49.880 --> 00:14:51.680
and to bring down your own curtain

00:14:52.160 --> 00:14:54.200
is what makes a true star performer.

00:15:21.160 --> 00:15:28.360
♪This world♪

00:15:28.760 --> 00:15:36.400
♪Has wronged me♪

00:15:36.400 --> 00:15:47.360
♪My innocent heart♪

00:15:53.280 --> 00:15:56.520
♪All my old kindness has been betrayed♪

00:15:56.520 --> 00:16:00.600
♪Bones in hills, my spirit torn♪

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:07.800
♪Heaven's flames undo the divine♪

00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:16.120
♪Oh heaven♪

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:23.640
♪Oh heaven♪

00:16:30.320 --> 00:16:35.840
♪Morning dew gleams♪

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:47.200
♪Washing dust, clearing my soul♪

00:16:47.320 --> 00:16:56.920
♪Moon by the cave lights ages past♪

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:02.920
♪I thought this world was bright in bloom♪

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:05.920
♪I thought this life was full of joy♪

00:17:05.920 --> 00:17:09.240
♪Now lamps dim, and the stars grow faint♪

00:17:09.320 --> 00:17:13.760
♪Now my eyes blur, all clarity gone♪

00:17:13.760 --> 00:17:17.040
♪This world has lost its rightful order♪

00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:20.640
♪Yet it is hard to steel my heart♪

00:17:21.240 --> 00:17:27.240
♪So be it, let my heart turn firm♪

00:17:27.560 --> 00:17:34.280
♪I rise to heaven to prove my loyal heart♪

00:17:34.280 --> 00:17:37.040
♪True in spirit, I rise to heaven♪

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:44.080
♪To prove my loyal heart♪

00:17:44.080 --> 00:17:53.560
♪To prove my loyal heart♪

00:18:34.260 --> 00:18:37.660
(Chinese Theatre and Opera Awards)

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:41.360
Bravo!

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:42.680
Bravo!

00:18:42.680 --> 00:18:44.600
Sis! Sis! Sis!

00:18:45.080 --> 00:18:47.440
Qinqiang opera star Yi Qin'e

00:18:47.440 --> 00:18:49.680
has become, since the award began,

00:18:49.680 --> 00:18:51.800
its youngest-ever winner.

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:53.400
(Qinqiang Opera Performer Yi Qin'e)
The play's success

00:18:53.400 --> 00:18:56.200
(Won Chinese Theatre and Opera Awards)
showed the charm of Qinqiang opera

00:18:56.520 --> 00:19:00.760
(Chinese Theatre)
and opened a bold Qinqiang chapter.

00:19:01.560 --> 00:19:03.960
I understand how everyone feels.

00:19:03.960 --> 00:19:06.680
Qin'e's performance was brilliant.

00:19:07.160 --> 00:19:09.000
But let's keep things orderly.

00:19:09.000 --> 00:19:10.320
Sign in an orderly line.

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:12.520
What is this?

00:19:12.520 --> 00:19:13.720
This lousy photo...

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:15.040
The color is too pale.

00:19:15.040 --> 00:19:16.440
Use new ones next time.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:17.520
Got it.

00:19:18.120 --> 00:19:20.600
Don't rush! Don't rush! Don't...

00:19:27.560 --> 00:19:28.840
(Eatery)
Ms. Yi Qin'e.

00:19:28.840 --> 00:19:31.280
They say drama mirrors life,

00:19:31.280 --> 00:19:32.320
so I'd like to ask,

00:19:32.320 --> 00:19:33.520
in Hu Xian Jie,

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:36.040
does the critique of life and its despair

00:19:36.040 --> 00:19:38.800
reflect your own outlook?

00:19:39.240 --> 00:19:41.320
I can't say if it does.

00:19:41.320 --> 00:19:42.400
But when I was performing...

00:19:42.400 --> 00:19:44.480
Listen. Your sister says it so well.

00:19:45.040 --> 00:19:46.280
Quiet. We're watching.

00:19:46.760 --> 00:19:48.400
Come on, drink up.

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:49.680
Uncle.

00:19:49.840 --> 00:19:51.760
But through this role, you

00:19:51.760 --> 00:19:53.520
won the top opera award.

00:19:53.520 --> 00:19:55.360
These folks are just drinking.

00:19:55.360 --> 00:19:56.760
Not even watching TV.

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:58.000
Brother.

00:19:58.560 --> 00:20:01.760
If they sing like Laidi does,

00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:04.720
that'd be top tier, right?

00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:07.400
I can't say if that's the top.

00:20:08.320 --> 00:20:10.720
Look at old Jiusuihong and Wei Changsheng.

00:20:11.040 --> 00:20:12.200
They were probably the same.

00:20:22.520 --> 00:20:23.360
Uncle.

00:20:23.720 --> 00:20:25.760
- Dad.
- Mom, why take their candy?

00:20:27.520 --> 00:20:28.720
We're eating pricey barbecue.

00:20:28.720 --> 00:20:30.320
What's wrong with a few sweets?

00:20:30.560 --> 00:20:32.040
You control everything?

00:20:32.720 --> 00:20:34.440
Those sweets aren't worth much.

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:36.160
Have some meat.

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:37.680
What? Am I making you look bad?

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:39.040
Easy, easy.

00:20:39.560 --> 00:20:41.200
- Eat this.
- Always eating.

00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:42.360
- Eat.
- No.

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:49.200
- Dad, cheers.
- Cheers.

00:20:49.240 --> 00:20:50.080
Cheers.

00:21:18.040 --> 00:21:18.880
Laidi.

00:21:19.840 --> 00:21:20.920
Can't sleep?

00:21:21.600 --> 00:21:23.200
Mom, you're still awake?

00:21:25.320 --> 00:21:28.200
Your sister snores louder than your dad.

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:30.760
How does Gao Wufu stand it?

00:21:34.280 --> 00:21:35.120
Laidi.

00:21:37.360 --> 00:21:39.760
The life you have now...

00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:42.840
I never even dared to dream of it.

00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:46.200
Back in the old days,

00:21:46.840 --> 00:21:49.000
it'd be fit for a queen.

00:21:50.800 --> 00:21:52.200
I never imagined it either.

00:21:53.040 --> 00:21:54.920
Your sister keeps complaining,

00:21:55.240 --> 00:21:56.920
saying that back then,

00:21:57.360 --> 00:21:59.360
your uncle should've taken her.

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:02.360
She says you stole her luck.

00:22:04.280 --> 00:22:06.160
She just doesn't get it.

00:22:06.920 --> 00:22:09.480
Even if your uncle had taken her,

00:22:10.560 --> 00:22:12.880
she couldn't be where you are today.

00:22:15.240 --> 00:22:17.400
What kind of life we get

00:22:18.680 --> 00:22:19.640
is up to fate.

00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:27.560
Laidi,

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:31.640
but still,

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:34.400
your sister has had it rough too.

00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:37.240
Last year, her medicinal herbs business

00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:39.360
lost a huge amount of money.

00:22:39.840 --> 00:22:41.720
Your sister's life now

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:43.280
is really hard.

00:22:44.400 --> 00:22:45.800
If you can help her,

00:22:46.640 --> 00:22:47.720
then give her a hand.

00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:51.680
And your brother

00:22:52.680 --> 00:22:54.480
can't stay in Jiuyangou anymore.

00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:57.400
All day, he wants to come to you.

00:22:58.240 --> 00:22:59.680
I've held him back for years.

00:23:00.560 --> 00:23:01.680
But the way things are going,

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:03.200
I can't stop him.

00:23:08.760 --> 00:23:10.920
We'll talk about him later.

00:23:11.880 --> 00:23:13.800
Focus on your own life first.

00:23:17.880 --> 00:23:19.200
After you're married,

00:23:20.040 --> 00:23:21.640
be more diligent.

00:23:23.360 --> 00:23:24.440
And be considerate.

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:27.280
Don't trouble Hongbing over everything.

00:23:28.880 --> 00:23:31.080
Whether a family can last

00:23:32.240 --> 00:23:34.160
mainly depends on the woman.

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:42.840
Kid.

00:23:44.840 --> 00:23:45.720
Give me your hand.

00:23:57.840 --> 00:23:59.280
Life isn't easy for women.

00:24:00.480 --> 00:24:02.320
I don't have much to give you.

00:24:04.040 --> 00:24:05.480
I just hope

00:24:07.280 --> 00:24:09.600
your life will be sweet.

00:24:32.120 --> 00:24:33.560
Good! Good!

00:24:35.360 --> 00:24:36.920
Everyone, quiet down, please.

00:24:37.400 --> 00:24:38.300
Hongbing.

00:24:38.320 --> 00:24:39.520
Give your dad and mom

00:24:39.520 --> 00:24:40.640
a bow too.

00:24:42.920 --> 00:24:44.600
Dad, Mom.

00:24:45.040 --> 00:24:47.160
We bow to you.

00:24:47.160 --> 00:24:48.520
Good!

00:24:49.840 --> 00:24:50.800
Good!

00:24:54.160 --> 00:24:55.880
Dad, Mom.

00:24:56.440 --> 00:24:59.000
Thank you for giving me
life and raising me.

00:24:59.520 --> 00:25:00.480
Don't cry.

00:25:00.720 --> 00:25:02.480
No tears on a day like this.

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:05.560
Hongbing, say something!

00:25:07.160 --> 00:25:09.160
Dad, Mom.

00:25:09.680 --> 00:25:10.880
Now Qin'e is mine to care.

00:25:11.230 --> 00:25:12.160
Just rest assured!

00:25:12.160 --> 00:25:13.320
Good!

00:25:15.680 --> 00:25:17.680
Hongbing, carry your bride!

00:25:17.680 --> 00:25:18.680
Let's head home!

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:19.800
Let's go!

00:25:20.120 --> 00:25:20.960
Pick her up!

00:25:21.840 --> 00:25:23.600
Pick her up!

00:25:23.600 --> 00:25:24.440
Come on.

00:25:26.520 --> 00:25:27.680
Let's go!

00:25:28.100 --> 00:25:30.300
(A match made in heaven)

00:25:42.820 --> 00:25:45.020
(Double happiness)

00:27:35.840 --> 00:27:36.840
Wonderful, wonderful.

00:27:37.440 --> 00:27:39.160
The wedding apartment looks beautiful.

00:27:39.160 --> 00:27:40.600
- It does?
- It sure does.

00:27:42.080 --> 00:27:43.240
I drank too much today.

00:27:43.240 --> 00:27:44.160
I'll head back.

00:27:44.160 --> 00:27:45.640
Okay, sir. I'll see you out.

00:27:45.800 --> 00:27:47.200
No need to see me out.

00:27:47.480 --> 00:27:48.560
Let Qin'e walk me out.

00:27:49.280 --> 00:27:50.960
She's the bride. I'll share her good luck.

00:27:50.960 --> 00:27:52.440
Right, right. Qin'e, go on.

00:27:52.440 --> 00:27:54.000
He must have something to say.

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:55.600
- Go on.
- Just downstairs.

00:27:56.840 --> 00:27:58.140
- Stay close. Watch your step.
- Okay.

00:27:58.160 --> 00:27:59.000
Qin'e, stay close.

00:27:59.470 --> 00:28:00.880
Okay. Take care.

00:28:03.600 --> 00:28:04.920
Finally, we can breathe.

00:28:05.720 --> 00:28:06.560
Qin'e.

00:28:07.240 --> 00:28:10.080
I really should congratulate you today.

00:28:10.720 --> 00:28:12.760
You've been with the
troupe for three years.

00:28:12.760 --> 00:28:13.920
These past years,

00:28:13.920 --> 00:28:15.640
I've watched you

00:28:15.640 --> 00:28:18.000
become the Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera.

00:28:18.680 --> 00:28:20.520
I bet, in the next three years,

00:28:20.920 --> 00:28:22.720
your future will still be wide open.

00:28:23.120 --> 00:28:24.080
Trust me on that.

00:28:25.320 --> 00:28:26.160
So,

00:28:26.680 --> 00:28:28.160
there's something I need to say.

00:28:28.160 --> 00:28:29.360
Don't think I'm nagging.

00:28:29.960 --> 00:28:30.840
I think...

00:28:30.840 --> 00:28:31.680
Troupe Leader.

00:28:32.160 --> 00:28:33.000
I know.

00:28:34.200 --> 00:28:35.920
I'm not having a baby yet.

00:28:36.240 --> 00:28:38.360
I'll sing with the troupe
for a few more years.

00:28:39.240 --> 00:28:40.240
That's great.

00:28:40.240 --> 00:28:42.120
Now I can finally relax.

00:28:43.840 --> 00:28:45.720
Reports say this group had long used

00:28:45.720 --> 00:28:46.760
the TV station as a cover,

00:28:46.840 --> 00:28:48.880
claiming to host
children's singing contests,

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:49.920
and moved across regions

00:28:49.920 --> 00:28:52.240
- What?
- and acquired fees by fraud.

00:28:52.240 --> 00:28:53.880
The total came to over 300,000 yuan.

00:28:54.400 --> 00:28:57.280
The main suspect, Mi,
was taken in at Nanjing.

00:28:57.280 --> 00:28:59.440
The case is still under review.

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:01.360
As people's

00:29:01.360 --> 00:29:02.800
living standards keep rising,

00:29:02.800 --> 00:29:04.320
their demand for cultural entertainment

00:29:04.320 --> 00:29:05.560
and child education

00:29:05.560 --> 00:29:06.760
is also growing.

00:29:06.760 --> 00:29:08.680
- But stay alert.
- Who is that?

00:29:08.680 --> 00:29:09.520
Don't fall into

00:29:09.520 --> 00:29:11.200
- Mi Lan?
- a trap that costs you all.

00:29:13.120 --> 00:29:14.320
That can't be.

00:29:17.040 --> 00:29:18.720
I've seen plenty of the lead types.

00:29:18.920 --> 00:29:21.160
And even more leading ladies.

00:29:21.800 --> 00:29:24.480
Life is short. Anything can happen.

00:29:25.160 --> 00:29:26.880
Right now, you need to hold on

00:29:26.880 --> 00:29:28.280
to whatever

00:29:28.280 --> 00:29:30.440
you can still control.

00:29:34.520 --> 00:29:35.960
Make the days ahead count.

00:29:37.360 --> 00:29:38.320
Don't see me off. Go back.

00:29:41.160 --> 00:29:42.000
Live well.

00:29:58.100 --> 00:30:03.220
(Double happiness)

00:30:10.800 --> 00:30:13.240
Tonight should have been the happiest

00:30:13.240 --> 00:30:15.120
day of Yi Qin'e's life,

00:30:15.640 --> 00:30:16.960
but for some reason,

00:30:17.480 --> 00:30:18.920
after all the cheering and joy,

00:30:19.320 --> 00:30:20.680
she felt a little uneasy.

00:30:21.680 --> 00:30:24.040
Afraid Heaven had given her so much

00:30:24.040 --> 00:30:25.320
more than she'd ever imagined,

00:30:25.720 --> 00:30:29.240
and would quietly plan to

00:30:29.640 --> 00:30:31.280
make her return it.

00:31:01.480 --> 00:31:02.320
Qin'e...

00:31:18.720 --> 00:31:21.240
Look here!

00:31:26.600 --> 00:31:27.440
It's made just for you.

00:31:28.240 --> 00:31:29.080
Do you like it?

00:31:32.280 --> 00:31:33.640
Why'd you do this?

00:31:34.120 --> 00:31:34.960
A waste of money.

00:31:35.960 --> 00:31:37.320
How can this be a waste?

00:31:38.000 --> 00:31:38.880
People say

00:31:39.120 --> 00:31:40.480
a star performer needs their own costume.

00:31:42.120 --> 00:31:43.480
When I first met you,

00:31:44.560 --> 00:31:45.520
you were Mu Guiying.

00:31:46.440 --> 00:31:48.360
Then I'll start with Mu Guiying.

00:31:52.000 --> 00:31:52.840
Okay.

00:31:52.960 --> 00:31:53.800
Take a look.

00:32:11.800 --> 00:32:12.640
Later on,

00:32:13.200 --> 00:32:14.160
once we save up some money,

00:32:15.080 --> 00:32:16.120
I'll get you another set.

00:32:16.800 --> 00:32:17.880
Li Huiniang's set.

00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:19.800
Yang Paifeng's.

00:32:19.920 --> 00:32:20.760
Bai Yunxian's.

00:32:21.760 --> 00:32:22.600
Whatever role you sing,

00:32:23.200 --> 00:32:24.160
I'll get it for you.

00:32:44.760 --> 00:32:45.840
During those days,

00:32:46.160 --> 00:32:48.480
Yi Qin'e was truly happy.

00:32:49.280 --> 00:32:50.640
Her married life was good.

00:32:50.840 --> 00:32:52.040
She didn't even notice

00:32:52.560 --> 00:32:53.640
the world outside

00:32:53.800 --> 00:32:55.160
had turned upside down.

00:32:56.280 --> 00:32:58.800
New trends were flooding in.

00:32:59.520 --> 00:33:02.040
Qinqiang opera, passed down for millennia,

00:33:02.520 --> 00:33:04.600
suddenly had almost no audience.

00:33:05.480 --> 00:33:07.120
As if overnight,

00:33:07.800 --> 00:33:10.640
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang Opera Theater)
shows dwindled like an ebbing tide.

00:33:11.760 --> 00:33:14.400
The troupe could pay only half wages.

00:33:15.080 --> 00:33:17.960
For the rest, they were on their own.

00:33:19.000 --> 00:33:21.360
And she was still lost in her honeymoon.

00:33:22.120 --> 00:33:24.360
(Two years later)
Fate doesn't wait for you.

00:33:24.560 --> 00:33:26.640
The baby arrived just like that.

00:33:27.320 --> 00:33:29.280
The trials meant for Yi Qin'e

00:33:29.280 --> 00:33:31.240
had only just begun.

00:33:49.600 --> 00:33:51.480
Why give water? What good is that?

00:33:51.480 --> 00:33:52.680
Feed him milk.

00:33:53.040 --> 00:33:54.480
The book says

00:33:54.480 --> 00:33:56.440
not to soothe a crying baby with milk.

00:33:56.880 --> 00:33:58.160
Or he'll never get off it.

00:33:58.680 --> 00:34:01.240
You can't raise a child by a book.

00:34:01.240 --> 00:34:03.120
He's so little. He needs milk.

00:34:03.520 --> 00:34:04.520
What kind of mom is this?

00:34:04.520 --> 00:34:05.360
Here, here.

00:34:05.640 --> 00:34:06.800
How can you

00:34:06.800 --> 00:34:08.120
not even calm your baby?

00:34:08.120 --> 00:34:08.960
There, there.

00:34:09.640 --> 00:34:10.480
There, there.

00:34:11.160 --> 00:34:12.640
Don't cry, baby. Don't cry.

00:34:17.440 --> 00:34:19.640
- My baby, don't cry.
- Why is his face so red?

00:34:20.560 --> 00:34:21.560
The book says

00:34:21.560 --> 00:34:23.440
a red face can be a warning sign.

00:34:23.440 --> 00:34:25.040
Stop reading that useless book.

00:34:26.120 --> 00:34:27.320
The kid is crying hard.

00:34:27.320 --> 00:34:28.600
Of course, the face is red.

00:34:29.640 --> 00:34:31.440
From the day we're born,

00:34:31.440 --> 00:34:32.880
life is one long struggle.

00:34:36.280 --> 00:34:38.080
Don't cry. There, there.

00:34:40.520 --> 00:34:42.880
A child wears everyone down.

00:34:43.400 --> 00:34:46.480
And marriage begins to crack

00:34:46.480 --> 00:34:48.520
in endless crying

00:34:48.840 --> 00:34:50.440
and trivial chores.

00:34:52.040 --> 00:34:53.160
Laidi.

00:34:53.360 --> 00:34:55.600
Look, you're on TV.

00:34:56.000 --> 00:34:58.280
Which play is it?

00:34:59.720 --> 00:35:01.240
Your mom looks great in it.

00:35:02.120 --> 00:35:03.680
Her singing's really good.

00:35:05.360 --> 00:35:06.240
Troupe Leader.

00:35:07.640 --> 00:35:08.480
Sanyuan.

00:35:08.560 --> 00:35:09.520
I was looking for you.

00:35:09.920 --> 00:35:10.760
Yeah?

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:12.360
How's Qin'e been lately?

00:35:13.200 --> 00:35:14.320
Same as always.

00:35:14.920 --> 00:35:16.080
At home, with the kid.

00:35:16.080 --> 00:35:17.280
The kid's still little.

00:35:17.840 --> 00:35:19.760
He's got the whole family worn out.

00:35:19.760 --> 00:35:21.280
Look at these dark circles.

00:35:21.560 --> 00:35:23.720
Why'd she have a kid so early?

00:35:23.720 --> 00:35:25.160
Right after she got married,

00:35:25.160 --> 00:35:26.520
down by her place,

00:35:26.520 --> 00:35:28.120
I told her straight up.

00:35:28.120 --> 00:35:29.920
"Wait a bit longer. Wait a bit longer."

00:35:30.240 --> 00:35:31.120
What was she thinking?

00:35:31.120 --> 00:35:32.600
Why'd she have a kid so early?

00:35:35.440 --> 00:35:36.600
She never even told me.

00:35:36.600 --> 00:35:38.560
Well... that's just how she is.

00:35:39.040 --> 00:35:40.560
She's always quiet.

00:35:40.560 --> 00:35:41.760
She tells no one a thing.

00:35:42.240 --> 00:35:44.040
She has her own ideas.

00:35:44.400 --> 00:35:45.300
Just look.

00:35:45.320 --> 00:35:46.640
At the height of her glory,

00:35:46.640 --> 00:35:47.840
she stepped away.

00:35:49.360 --> 00:35:50.600
That kid was meant for it.

00:35:51.520 --> 00:35:53.040
She caught Qinqiang opera in its prime,

00:35:53.240 --> 00:35:55.000
and missed its decline.

00:35:55.520 --> 00:35:57.280
We took Hu Xian Jie south

00:35:57.280 --> 00:35:58.680
for those last few shows.

00:35:58.680 --> 00:35:59.720
After we came back,

00:35:59.720 --> 00:36:01.200
the troupe had lost its heart.

00:36:01.720 --> 00:36:03.720
Everyone had seen it for real,

00:36:03.720 --> 00:36:04.840
the prosperity down south.

00:36:04.840 --> 00:36:06.560
We wondered what we'd been doing all along.

00:36:06.920 --> 00:36:08.440
Everyone's heart is unsettled.

00:36:08.760 --> 00:36:10.480
I didn't even know what to do.

00:36:10.800 --> 00:36:12.600
There's a new term now, right?

00:36:12.600 --> 00:36:14.960
Qinqiang opera is a traditional folk culture.

00:36:15.240 --> 00:36:16.720
Will things get better later?

00:36:17.200 --> 00:36:18.160
I don't care about later.

00:36:18.160 --> 00:36:19.280
I only care about right now.

00:36:19.720 --> 00:36:20.920
There's one thing right now.

00:36:21.200 --> 00:36:23.040
You must get Qin'e back.

00:36:23.040 --> 00:36:24.600
If she won't come back to sing,

00:36:24.600 --> 00:36:25.680
Qinqiang opera is finished.

00:36:27.760 --> 00:36:28.640
I'll talk to her.

00:36:29.120 --> 00:36:29.960
I will.

00:36:35.240 --> 00:36:36.080
What?

00:36:36.640 --> 00:36:37.480
I don't need it.

00:36:38.280 --> 00:36:40.520
The troupe still pays 30% wages.

00:36:40.520 --> 00:36:41.360
I won't starve.

00:36:41.760 --> 00:36:42.800
This is the deposit.

00:36:44.680 --> 00:36:46.280
The troupe has booked a show.

00:36:46.840 --> 00:36:49.040
It's the provincial Guanzhong Trade Fair.

00:36:49.960 --> 00:36:51.880
A real gig, and the pay is good.

00:36:52.200 --> 00:36:53.080
500 per show.

00:36:53.520 --> 00:36:54.760
Star performers can get extra.

00:36:55.280 --> 00:36:56.120
I can't go.

00:36:56.480 --> 00:36:57.320
Why not?

00:36:57.920 --> 00:36:59.440
The baby isn't weaned yet.

00:36:59.720 --> 00:37:01.360
And Hongbing is busy with work.

00:37:01.440 --> 00:37:04.080
If I go, Mom can't manage alone.

00:37:04.800 --> 00:37:06.160
Take the baby with you.

00:37:07.160 --> 00:37:09.360
Your fans have missed you for ages.

00:37:10.040 --> 00:37:11.360
Then I really shouldn't go.

00:37:12.360 --> 00:37:13.880
Look at me now.

00:37:15.440 --> 00:37:17.320
Better they remember me as I was.

00:37:19.760 --> 00:37:20.720
Think it over.

00:37:22.120 --> 00:37:23.280
You've still got a few days.

00:37:23.600 --> 00:37:24.920
Decide for yourself.

00:37:40.160 --> 00:37:41.000
Comrades,

00:37:42.320 --> 00:37:44.040
over a decade of Reform and Opening-Up,

00:37:45.160 --> 00:37:46.600
here in Beishan,

00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:48.480
we've made era-defining progress.

00:37:48.840 --> 00:37:50.760
Back in 1978,

00:37:50.760 --> 00:37:53.640
the county's GDP was just over ten million.

00:37:54.320 --> 00:37:56.960
Last year, it topped one hundred million.

00:37:57.320 --> 00:37:59.840
This year, we will unite and forge ahead.

00:38:00.240 --> 00:38:01.840
It'll be a year of huge progress!

00:38:01.840 --> 00:38:03.080
- Good.
- Good.

00:38:03.080 --> 00:38:03.920
Good.

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:06.280
Stand up. Up.

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:08.200
Come on, everyone up. Stand up.

00:38:08.600 --> 00:38:09.640
Let's chant the slogan.

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:10.760
Hongbing.

00:38:10.880 --> 00:38:13.120
Isn't that slogan a bit much?

00:38:13.800 --> 00:38:14.880
If you don't make it big,

00:38:14.880 --> 00:38:16.280
how will you get his attention?

00:38:16.880 --> 00:38:18.240
All you do is make snide remarks

00:38:18.240 --> 00:38:19.280
all day long.

00:38:19.600 --> 00:38:20.880
Come on, let's practice together.

00:38:20.960 --> 00:38:22.880
United as one!

00:38:22.880 --> 00:38:24.080
- Liu Hongbing!
- United...

00:38:24.640 --> 00:38:25.640
What are you doing?

00:38:27.120 --> 00:38:28.320
Everyone, listen to me.

00:38:28.320 --> 00:38:29.840
Just hear me out, okay?

00:38:30.600 --> 00:38:32.960
Beishan's district lines have changed.

00:38:33.280 --> 00:38:35.630
It will be run by Qinchuan now.

00:38:36.160 --> 00:38:38.960
And our administrative office faces cuts.

00:38:38.960 --> 00:38:41.400
This wasn't decided on a whim.

00:38:41.710 --> 00:38:42.600
So,

00:38:42.600 --> 00:38:44.440
please try to understand, okay?

00:38:44.440 --> 00:38:46.160
- Try to understand.
- What about us?

00:38:46.160 --> 00:38:47.240
We need to make a living!

00:38:48.960 --> 00:38:49.960
Let me say something.

00:38:50.600 --> 00:38:51.640
If you cut us loose,

00:38:52.240 --> 00:38:53.320
what are we supposed to do?

00:38:53.880 --> 00:38:56.000
- We need to make a living!
- Exactly!

00:38:56.000 --> 00:38:56.920
- Right!
- That's true!

00:38:56.920 --> 00:38:58.800
Who said you'd be left with nothing?

00:38:59.920 --> 00:39:01.160
The leaders have considered

00:39:01.160 --> 00:39:02.720
everyone's livelihood.

00:39:03.000 --> 00:39:04.760
So they've set aside funds

00:39:04.760 --> 00:39:06.040
for a service-year buyout.

00:39:06.040 --> 00:39:07.720
For under 25 years of service,

00:39:07.720 --> 00:39:09.080
you get 10,000 yuan outright.

00:39:09.080 --> 00:39:10.400
For 30 years of service,

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:12.320
you get 20,000 yuan outright.

00:39:12.600 --> 00:39:13.600
It's only that much.

00:39:13.600 --> 00:39:14.440
Liu Hongbing!

00:39:14.920 --> 00:39:15.760
Liu Hongbing.

00:39:16.360 --> 00:39:17.440
If you can't be reasonable,

00:39:17.680 --> 00:39:19.840
fine, keep stirring things up.

00:39:20.840 --> 00:39:23.280
Then even that 10 or 20 grand is gone.

00:39:23.280 --> 00:39:24.320
What will you do?

00:39:24.640 --> 00:39:26.000
They'll still do things their way!

00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:27.840
- You're leaving?
- That's it?

00:39:29.440 --> 00:39:30.400
I'm telling you all,

00:39:30.880 --> 00:39:32.080
the tide of the times is here.

00:39:32.640 --> 00:39:33.720
Nobody can stand against it!

00:39:35.240 --> 00:39:36.320
You can't just leave!

00:39:36.480 --> 00:39:37.960
Give us an explanation!

00:39:40.200 --> 00:39:42.120
Hongbing, what do we do?

00:39:42.120 --> 00:39:44.360
- What now?
- We're with you. Say something.

00:39:44.360 --> 00:39:45.720
- Go on.
- What do we do now?

00:39:45.720 --> 00:39:47.400
Hongbing, give everyone a call.

00:39:47.400 --> 00:39:49.080
- Yeah, Hongbing.
- Say something.

00:39:52.800 --> 00:39:54.160
Planned economy.

00:39:54.200 --> 00:39:55.760
Market economy.

00:39:55.880 --> 00:39:57.200
Streamlining and downsizing.

00:39:57.240 --> 00:39:59.760
Laid off. Starting over.

00:40:00.400 --> 00:40:01.560
Back then,

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:03.320
big newspaper headlines

00:40:03.320 --> 00:40:04.720
and TV slogans

00:40:04.920 --> 00:40:06.960
were taking turns to speak and sing.

00:40:07.880 --> 00:40:09.720
The tide of the times had arrived.

00:40:10.240 --> 00:40:12.040
No one could stand on the shore,

00:40:12.320 --> 00:40:13.880
being easy and calm.

00:40:14.640 --> 00:40:15.800
Yi Qin'e knew

00:40:16.120 --> 00:40:18.480
everyone would be changed.

00:40:23.440 --> 00:40:24.280
Sir.

00:40:25.080 --> 00:40:26.120
I... I won't take it.

00:40:26.120 --> 00:40:26.960
You go.

00:40:27.200 --> 00:40:29.000
- Sorry.
- What's your issue?

00:41:04.280 --> 00:41:05.880
Mom. Qin'e.

00:41:06.920 --> 00:41:07.760
I'm back.

00:41:09.960 --> 00:41:10.800
Mom.

00:41:11.320 --> 00:41:12.160
Here's the fish.

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:16.760
I told you to buy crucian carp.

00:41:16.760 --> 00:41:17.840
This isn't crucian carp.

00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:19.120
It won't help with milk.

00:41:19.120 --> 00:41:20.320
Isn't it?

00:41:20.320 --> 00:41:21.760
The fish seller said it was.

00:41:23.080 --> 00:41:24.000
It really isn't?

00:41:25.280 --> 00:41:26.280
Eat this first.

00:41:26.280 --> 00:41:27.360
I'll buy her some tomorrow.

00:41:29.880 --> 00:41:31.880
The baby's here.

00:41:32.720 --> 00:41:33.920
- Come here.
- I just calmed him.

00:41:33.920 --> 00:41:35.000
Don't make him cry again.

00:41:35.720 --> 00:41:38.280
Okay, come here. Daddy's got you.

00:41:39.560 --> 00:41:40.840
Daddy's got you.

00:41:42.280 --> 00:41:43.880
He doesn't even know crucian carp.

00:41:45.280 --> 00:41:46.920
Such a pampered young master.

00:41:47.400 --> 00:41:48.720
Who are we raising the kid for?

00:41:49.240 --> 00:41:51.560
Had fun with Mommy all day, huh?

00:41:53.560 --> 00:41:54.400
Qin'e.

00:41:55.480 --> 00:41:57.240
Take him to the hospital tomorrow.

00:41:57.240 --> 00:41:58.080
For what?

00:41:58.520 --> 00:41:59.400
I just feel

00:41:59.800 --> 00:42:01.160
the kid seems a bit off.

00:42:01.480 --> 00:42:02.960
What do you mean, "off"?

00:42:03.600 --> 00:42:05.560
He cries a lot. That's off?

00:42:05.560 --> 00:42:06.840
You won't talk to your dad.

00:42:06.840 --> 00:42:07.880
You two are off too?

00:42:10.360 --> 00:42:11.400
Why start a fight?

00:42:11.880 --> 00:42:12.720
What I mean is

00:42:12.720 --> 00:42:14.520
I feel the kid's a bit behind.

00:42:14.880 --> 00:42:16.160
Compared with kids his age,

00:42:16.480 --> 00:42:17.680
he doesn't talk much.

00:42:17.680 --> 00:42:18.920
Who said that?

00:42:20.000 --> 00:42:21.680
My kid doesn't need a comparison.

00:42:21.960 --> 00:42:23.320
Why care how others are?

00:42:23.920 --> 00:42:24.760
Fine, fine.

00:42:25.240 --> 00:42:27.240
If you think he's fine, then fine.

00:42:28.600 --> 00:42:29.480
Baby,

00:42:30.000 --> 00:42:31.880
listen to Mom.

00:42:32.160 --> 00:42:33.560
It's okay, it's okay.

00:42:36.800 --> 00:42:38.560
- Listen to Mom.
- How's work?

00:42:40.680 --> 00:42:41.520
What?

00:42:41.600 --> 00:42:42.840
How's work going?

00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:44.600
What about work?

00:42:45.120 --> 00:42:46.840
Aren't they redeploying and laying off?

00:42:49.960 --> 00:42:52.760
They won't lay off
Young Master Liu, okay?

00:42:53.960 --> 00:42:54.840
That's good.

00:42:58.840 --> 00:43:00.080
- What happened?
- Why did it blow up?

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.680 --> 00:43:10.520
Chu Jiahe.

00:43:11.000 --> 00:43:13.200
Over the years, I've
done every kind of job.

00:43:13.450 --> 00:43:15.160
I've been down on my luck.

00:43:15.400 --> 00:43:17.280
He had a cerebral hemorrhage.

00:43:17.520 --> 00:43:19.000
Now he ended up like this.

00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:19.980
Dad.

00:43:21.160 --> 00:43:22.840
Uncle, I'm feeling nervous.

00:43:22.920 --> 00:43:24.530
Nervous? You've performed on stages

00:43:24.710 --> 00:43:25.620
much bigger than this.

00:43:25.800 --> 00:43:27.960
People now hire modern
song-and-dance shows

00:43:28.320 --> 00:43:30.030
for weddings and funerals.

00:43:30.280 --> 00:43:32.400
Who still watches the
old-style Qinqiang opera?

00:43:33.220 --> 00:43:35.220
(Black Rose Song and Dance Troupe)

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪